tourBios.carHigh: 2015: T12 at the California Qualifying Tournament shooting rounds of 71-68-74-79. Season-best outing was a T11 at The Great Waterway Classic.
tourBios.personal: Favorite course he's played is PGA National and hopes to play Augusta National...Favorite pro sports teams are the Cardinals, Pacers, and Colts...Dream foursome would include Tiger Woods, Jack Nicklaus and Miguel Jimenez...Twitter name is @davmills.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA T was T11th in 2015 at the The Great Waterway Classic.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks 94th in Scoring Average (Actual) on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA TOUR Canada.
